name: Starfall (SkiZzal)
description:
Try to get to the finish without getting pulled into the stars!

PRESS R TO RESTART!!

This is the first game I've made in the Godot engine, so it's pretty simple but I think it came out alright. If I had more time, I would definitely add more levels because the ones I had time to make were pretty underwhelming IMO and I think this game has more potential.
